func update_application():
    show_text("Updating V-Sekai... Please wait.")
    if Velopack.check_for_updates():
        Velopack.perform_update()
    hide_text()
    notify("Update complete!")

func show_text(text):
    var label = Label.new()
    label.text = text
    add_child(label)

func hide_text():
    get_node("Label").queue_free()

func notify(message):
    show_message(message)

In “V-Sekai: My Life as a Princess,” players assume the role of a princess tasked with rebuilding and managing a kingdom. The game focuses on relaxation through planning, resource management, VR interactions, and adventurer tasking.



Lateral Thinking with Weathered Technology
Designed so both planning and people can do the same things




